const getCountryFlag = function getCountryFlag(country: string) {
  country = country?.toLowerCase();
  const nations = countries.filter(v => {
    return v.name?.toLowerCase() === country || v.code?.toLowerCase() === country;
  });
  let image = null;
  if(nations.length > 0){
    image = require('./../assets/images/flag-icons-main/'+nations[0].flag_4X3);
  }
  return image;
};

export default getCountryFlag;

const countries: { code: string; name: string; flag_4X3: string }[] = [
  { code: "af", name: "Afghanistan", flag_4X3: "flags/4x3/af.svg" },
